1
00:00:02,360 --> 00:00:04,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What... is this?</i></font>

2
00:00:04,580 --> 00:00:08,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel as if my soul's been flung 
somewhere unimaginably far...</i></font>

3
00:00:13,270 --> 00:00:17,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Has it truly been a thousand 
years since we last assembled?</i></font>

4
00:00:18,750 --> 00:00:21,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We have not since the Silver Age.</i></font>

5
00:00:22,860 --> 00:00:25,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The one back then was 
exceptional, as well.</i></font>

6
00:00:25,220 --> 00:00:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The one who, at level 255,</i></font>

7
00:00:27,060 --> 00:00:31,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>tamed all four of us and 
returned our powers to us.</i></font>

8
00:00:31,800 --> 00:00:33,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How...</i></font>

9
00:00:33,150 --> 00:00:36,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've never heard these voices 
before, but I know them.</i></font>

10
00:00:36,980 --> 00:00:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The day will soon come</i></font>

11
00:00:40,250 --> 00:00:43,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>when we all come together and 
fully regain our powers.</i></font>

12
00:00:43,450 --> 00:00:46,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It will be the most auspicious day 
since the moment of creation!</i></font>

13
00:00:47,250 --> 00:00:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My goodness. You seem 
quite fond of this boy,</font>

14
00:00:51,250 --> 00:00:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Mad Dog" Leviathan.</font>

15
00:01:01,530 --> 00:01:04,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was I... hearing things?</i></font>

16
00:01:04,890 --> 00:01:06,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A voice from the heavens...</font>

17
00:01:07,830 --> 00:01:09,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was God's voice, wasn't it?!</font>

18
00:01:08,900 --> 00:01:10,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I heard it, too!</font>

19
00:01:09,490 --> 00:01:12,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The heavens have placed their 
hopes in the Thirteenth Prince!</font>

20
00:01:10,610 --> 00:01:11,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Incredible!</font>

21
00:01:17,620 --> 00:01:19,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard it, too.</font>

22
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impressive, boy.
This is a happy occasion!</font>

23
00:01:23,270 --> 00:01:24,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You, too, Prince Indra?</font>

24
00:01:25,190 --> 00:01:26,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gigi.</font>

25
00:01:26,230 --> 00:01:27,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes?</font>

26
00:01:27,860 --> 00:01:32,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give five... no, ten rean to 
everyone standing around here.</font>

27
00:01:32,950 --> 00:01:35,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}All hail the Wise Prince!</font>

28
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Master!</font>

29
00:01:35,140 --> 00:01:36,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

30
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:41,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Banzai! Banzai! Banzai!</font>

31
00:01:36,910 --> 00:01:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He is truly the one
acknowledged by the divine!</font>

32
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:43,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>On an auspicious day,</i></font>

33
00:01:42,770 --> 00:01:44,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Here you go!</font>

34
00:01:43,830 --> 00:01:47,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>a time when something good happens,</i></font>

35
00:01:47,490 --> 00:01:49,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>it is considered the duty
of the nobility to share it</i></font>

36
00:01:49,830 --> 00:01:52,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>with everyone rather than
keep it all to themselves.</i></font>

37
00:01:53,510 --> 00:01:57,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It is said that third-rate 
nobles oppose this,</i></font>

38
00:01:57,660 --> 00:02:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>second-rate nobles go along 
with it out of sheer pride,</i></font>

39
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:05,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and first-rate nobles just do it as 
if it's the natural course of action.</i></font>

40
00:02:09,510 --> 00:02:11,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I may, Wise Prince...</font>

41
00:02:11,830 --> 00:02:14,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please allow me to refuse 
this aid you have offered.</font>

42
00:02:15,730 --> 00:02:16,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

43
00:02:17,430 --> 00:02:20,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I wish to become your knight.</font>

44
00:02:20,090 --> 00:02:22,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To do that, I must 
advance on my own merit</font>

45
00:02:22,860 --> 00:02:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and become worthy of 
living in your service.</font>

46
00:02:26,790 --> 00:02:27,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Denied.</font>

47
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:29,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

48
00:02:29,860 --> 00:02:32,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To accept help and then slack 
off would be inexcusable,</font>

49
00:02:32,670 --> 00:02:35,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but only second-rate knights 
accept out of sheer pride.</font>

50
00:02:36,130 --> 00:02:37,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Second-rate?</font>

51
00:02:37,500 --> 00:02:41,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to be first-rate,
do not be ashamed to accept aid.</font>

52
00:02:41,610 --> 00:02:43,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just give even more back to your master.</font>

53
00:02:45,540 --> 00:02:48,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to be worthy of me, 
that's what you need to do.</font>

54
00:02:49,620 --> 00:02:51,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood!</font>

55
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:57,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impressive. It only took 
one well-spoken line.</font>

56
00:02:58,370 --> 00:03:01,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's grown into one intriguing little sprout.</font>

57
00:03:01,420 --> 00:03:03,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brilliant, is he not?</font>

58
00:03:06,330 --> 00:03:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is why I thought...</font>

59
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:15,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">your granddaughter would 
be perfect for him.</font>

60
00:03:36,500 --> 00:03:38,500
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#817c4f"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="10">Born Blessed, So I'll Obtain Ultimate Power</font></b></font></font></font>

61
00:03:36,500 --> 00:03:38,500
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#051529">m 0 0 l 235 0 l 225 8 l 235 15 l 18 15 l 30 8 l 18 0</font></font>

62
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:56,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We are outside the palace.
No need for excessive formalities.</font>

63
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:59,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uncle, stand beside me.</font>

64
00:04:59,580 --> 00:05:00,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

65
00:05:09,690 --> 00:05:11,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And now, Leviathan.</i></font>

66
00:05:11,780 --> 00:05:13,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just slight menace.</i></font>

67
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:16,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Only enough to inspire awe and respect.</i></font>

68
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:19,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Good. I don't sense any treachery.</i></font>

69
00:05:19,340 --> 00:05:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So melodramatic.</font>

70
00:05:21,590 --> 00:05:25,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm surprised he can keep his 
cool at such a young age.</font>

71
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:29,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's gotta be the number 
one prince, right?</font>

72
00:05:29,060 --> 00:05:32,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is why I called him the "Wise."</font>

73
00:05:32,110 --> 00:05:35,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just as fitting as 
your "Lightning," no?</font>

74
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:40,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be just a thundering old 
fart soon enough, though.</font>

75
00:05:40,850 --> 00:05:43,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noah will grow into his "Wise" title.</font>

76
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:47,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It has been determined that he will make 
his first campaign alone, after all.</font>

77
00:05:49,450 --> 00:05:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A solo first campaign?!</font>

78
00:05:51,500 --> 00:05:54,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't they normally take a robust escort?</font>

79
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:57,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But with this one, I can believe it.</font>

80
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:59,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The people have turned 
their attention to me.</i></font>

81
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This would be an opportune 
time to escort His Majesty.</i></font>

82
00:06:03,430 --> 00:06:05,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, could it be...</i></font>

83
00:06:07,580 --> 00:06:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I knew it. Then I'll 
gladly accept his favor.</i></font>

84
00:06:10,460 --> 00:06:13,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is what's so amazing about Noah.</font>

85
00:06:14,300 --> 00:06:19,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you all that to create an 
opportunity for him to escort me.</font>

86
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:22,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He understood that and leapt on board.</font>

87
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:25,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? Impressive.</font>

88
00:06:25,850 --> 00:06:28,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't even notice.</font>

89
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:32,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As free-wheeling as you are, 
you lack sensitivity.</font>

90
00:06:32,270 --> 00:06:35,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why you and your wife quarrel 
endlessly over trivial things.</font>

91
00:06:37,660 --> 00:06:39,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got that right!</font>

92
00:06:39,380 --> 00:06:42,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All the more reason to feel at 
ease giving him my granddaughter!</font>

93
00:06:47,820 --> 00:06:50,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, Uncle, we must talk.</font>

94
00:07:02,410 --> 00:07:05,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what'd you wanna talk about?</font>

95
00:07:06,060 --> 00:07:07,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

96
00:07:09,660 --> 00:07:10,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Luthier.</i></font>

97
00:07:23,550 --> 00:07:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I will disinherit 
the crown prince.</font>

98
00:07:26,610 --> 00:07:31,510
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#0b0700">Episode 11</font></b></font></font>

99
00:07:26,610 --> 00:07:31,510
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#0b0700">Disinheritance</font></b></font></font>

100
00:07:38,590 --> 00:07:41,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had hoped things would work out,</font>

101
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:45,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I've been left with no 
choice but to deem him unfit.</font>

102
00:07:45,310 --> 00:07:46,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

103
00:07:46,730 --> 00:07:48,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The matter with Gilbert.</font>

104
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:50,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

105
00:07:51,730 --> 00:07:54,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I couldn't let His Majesty 
kill his own child,</i></font>

106
00:07:54,940 --> 00:07:59,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so I tried to convince him to give 
Gilbert no more than a life sentence.</i></font>

107
00:08:00,790 --> 00:08:02,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But then the crown prince...</i></font>

108
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:06,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That in itself was not a mistake,</font>

109
00:08:06,550 --> 00:08:09,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but there must have been some 
other way to go about it.</font>

110
00:08:09,970 --> 00:08:12,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That scared the hell outta me, too.</font>

111
00:08:12,860 --> 00:08:17,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he were to become the emperor, 
there'd definitely be a major purge.</font>

112
00:08:17,340 --> 00:08:18,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

113
00:08:18,470 --> 00:08:22,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In particular, Henry, Oscar, and Noah 
would be the first ones eliminated.</font>

114
00:08:22,980 --> 00:08:25,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Such pettiness and cruelty...</font>

115
00:08:25,940 --> 00:08:29,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I cannot allow such a man to succeed me.</font>

116
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:32,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's fine, but what's next?</font>

117
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:35,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's gonna be the next crown prince?</font>

118
00:08:35,010 --> 00:08:36,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't decided.</font>

119
00:08:36,770 --> 00:08:40,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't be like that. 
You're an old man now.</font>

120
00:08:40,470 --> 00:08:45,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you drop dead before you choose 
an heir, it'll divide the nation.</font>

121
00:08:48,890 --> 00:08:51,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His Majesty must have 
come to Indra for advice</i></font>

122
00:08:51,820 --> 00:08:54,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>because no one else could 
be so frank with him.</i></font>

123
00:08:55,890 --> 00:08:58,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To say I haven't decided is inaccurate.</font>

124
00:08:58,590 --> 00:09:03,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if I announce my decision now, 
it would only lead to more feuding.</font>

125
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:06,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's still better than leaving 
the crown prince's post vacant.</font>

126
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:07,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True.</font>

127
00:09:08,580 --> 00:09:10,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I may speak, Your Majesty...</font>

128
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

129
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:16,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps you could tell the public only 
that you have prepared your will...</font>

130
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:21,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and that the name of your 
heir is written in it.</font>

131
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:23,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That won't work.</font>

132
00:09:23,490 --> 00:09:27,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyone could forge a 
will after he's dead.</font>

133
00:09:27,070 --> 00:09:32,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, which is why His Majesty would 
hide his will inside his body.</font>

134
00:09:33,890 --> 00:09:37,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A simple example would be a false 
tooth with writing engraved in it,</font>

135
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:39,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or perhaps some sort of magic...</font>

136
00:09:40,460 --> 00:09:45,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get it. If it's on his person at 
all times, no one can change it.</font>

137
00:09:46,570 --> 00:09:50,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remarkable, Noah! That is a fine idea!</font>

138
00:09:57,330 --> 00:09:59,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wait outside, as well.</font>

139
00:09:59,900 --> 00:10:01,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let no one enter.</font>

140
00:10:01,750 --> 00:10:02,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sire.</font>

141
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's he?</font>

142
00:10:04,370 --> 00:10:05,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to worry.</font>

143
00:10:06,290 --> 00:10:09,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He is a liaison, the sort who is always 
present at occasions of this nature.</font>

144
00:10:09,700 --> 00:10:13,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He cannot hear, speak, or read.</font>

145
00:10:16,380 --> 00:10:18,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will take my leave now.</font>

146
00:10:23,270 --> 00:10:27,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, Noah, you've made 
an excellent proposal.</font>

147
00:10:27,150 --> 00:10:28,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've decided to employ it.</font>

148
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:31,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sire. Also, one other thing...</font>

149
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:34,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think command of our full military 
should be returned to you,</font>

150
00:10:34,740 --> 00:10:37,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">including Henry's post as 
minister-prince of military affairs</font>

151
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and mine as governor-general 
of the first imperial guard.</font>

152
00:10:41,070 --> 00:10:45,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good point. If anyone who objects to 
his will is in command of any forces,</font>

153
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:49,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he could remove all the others 
and install himself as emperor.</font>

154
00:10:49,390 --> 00:10:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A sound argument...</font>

155
00:10:51,760 --> 00:10:55,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I wouldn't have expected it from 
one of the guys who'll lose his post.</font>

156
00:10:55,540 --> 00:10:57,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impressive, boy.</font>

157
00:10:57,380 --> 00:10:59,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll make a fine husband 
for your granddaughter, no?</font>

158
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:01,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He sure will.</font>

159
00:11:05,810 --> 00:11:09,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An edict expressing gratitude to me while 
relieving me of my governor-general post.</i></font>

160
00:11:14,690 --> 00:11:16,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And that one will be for Henry.</i></font>

161
00:11:22,770 --> 00:11:25,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was an awfully simplistic order.</i></font>

162
00:11:25,450 --> 00:11:28,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I suppose he's been trained 
so that he can only carry out</i></font>

163
00:11:28,470 --> 00:11:30,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>a certain few specific orders.</i></font>

164
00:11:30,410 --> 00:11:33,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So how are you gonna handle the 
crown prince's disinheritance?</font>

165
00:11:38,910 --> 00:11:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In my opinion as minister-prince 
of justice,</font>

166
00:11:41,630 --> 00:11:43,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that's entirely up to you.</font>

167
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:50,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty is free to name or 
disinherit your heir as you please.</font>

168
00:11:50,710 --> 00:11:53,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one can meddle in your decision.</font>

169
00:11:53,860 --> 00:11:55,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

170
00:11:55,310 --> 00:12:02,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But unlike Gilbert, Albert has not 
committed a specific offense.</font>

171
00:12:02,110 --> 00:12:06,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For that reason, it may be best to 
let him remain a prince, at least.</font>

172
00:12:06,650 --> 00:12:09,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then how about this?</font>

173
00:12:09,180 --> 00:12:12,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Albert has not committed treason 
against me or the empire,</font>

174
00:12:12,370 --> 00:12:14,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but he is not capable enough for 
me to entrust the empire to him.</font>

175
00:12:14,930 --> 00:12:17,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He will thus be stripped of
his role as crown prince,</font>

176
00:12:17,130 --> 00:12:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but retain the title of prince."</font>

177
00:12:18,790 --> 00:12:20,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think that sounds excellent.</font>

178
00:12:20,620 --> 00:12:23,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great. So, emperor,</font>

179
00:12:23,510 --> 00:12:26,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">does Albert have any chance 
of becoming your heir again?</font>

180
00:12:26,630 --> 00:12:27,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

181
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:34,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He really has given up on Albert.</i></font>

182
00:12:34,520 --> 00:12:37,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you should probably make that clear.</font>

183
00:12:39,060 --> 00:12:41,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps you could give him a title?</font>

184
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:44,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One like "Ended Prince," for
example, implying that he</font>

185
00:12:44,650 --> 00:12:46,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">cannot advance beyond "prince"?</font>

186
00:12:46,110 --> 00:12:47,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

187
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:49,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I like that.</font>

188
00:12:49,890 --> 00:12:52,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noah, thank you for your counsel.</font>

189
00:12:55,830 --> 00:12:58,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm... This won't do...</font>

190
00:12:58,450 --> 00:13:02,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the deal?
That's a lot of mistakes.</font>

191
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:05,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the writing's so convoluted, 
no one'll understand it.</font>

192
00:13:05,380 --> 00:13:06,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong with you?</font>

193
00:13:06,820 --> 00:13:09,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm taking my son's inheritance away.</font>

194
00:13:09,800 --> 00:13:12,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if this isn't as 
grave as taking his life,</font>

195
00:13:12,900 --> 00:13:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can hardly bear it.</font>

196
00:13:16,750 --> 00:13:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get it.</font>

197
00:13:18,590 --> 00:13:22,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just keep redoing it until you 
can write it without hesitation.</font>

198
00:13:22,870 --> 00:13:25,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty, if I may...</font>

199
00:13:26,210 --> 00:13:30,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps you should leave what 
you've written exactly as it is?</font>

200
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:33,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It will remain on the record 
as an official edict,</font>

201
00:13:34,070 --> 00:13:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so your feelings will be preserved 
in a way that Albert can see them.</font>

202
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if he can accept that</font>

203
00:13:40,340 --> 00:13:44,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and continue to push on as a 
prince for the empire's sake...</font>

204
00:13:44,880 --> 00:13:47,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If only you had been...</font>

205
00:13:51,220 --> 00:13:54,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will do that. Excellent advice.</font>

206
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:56,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Your Majesty.</font>

207
00:14:12,540 --> 00:14:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it!</font>

208
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it, boy?</font>

209
00:14:15,750 --> 00:14:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This eunuch visibly reacted 
after looking at the edict.</font>

210
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:20,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

211
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:22,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then he hesitated.</font>

212
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:24,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because he knows what it says.</font>

213
00:14:26,060 --> 00:14:27,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won't escape!</font>

214
00:14:31,070 --> 00:14:32,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cruz!</font>

215
00:14:32,260 --> 00:14:34,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-Is something the matter?</font>

216
00:14:35,310 --> 00:14:37,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That man can read.</font>

217
00:14:37,980 --> 00:14:39,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha—</font>

218
00:14:41,740 --> 00:14:43,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a result of my own negligence!</font>

219
00:14:43,650 --> 00:14:45,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please... Please forgive me!</font>

220
00:14:45,950 --> 00:14:47,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How shall he be punished, Noah?</font>

221
00:14:47,990 --> 00:14:51,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Execution. To be carried out immediately.</font>

222
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:52,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The reason?</font>

223
00:14:52,820 --> 00:14:55,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He lied about being unable to read</font>

224
00:14:55,060 --> 00:14:58,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so he could assume what could be 
considered a key role in the empire.</font>

225
00:14:58,230 --> 00:15:01,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has sullied
Your Majesty's imperial court.</font>

226
00:15:01,580 --> 00:15:04,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shouldn't we get some information 
out of him before we kill him?</font>

227
00:15:05,680 --> 00:15:07,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That would tell us who is behind this,</font>

228
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:10,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">making it possible to 
punish them both, but...</font>

229
00:15:11,040 --> 00:15:12,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What if it was Albert?</i></font>

230
00:15:13,150 --> 00:15:16,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Or one of the other princes?</i></font>

231
00:15:16,050 --> 00:15:17,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

232
00:15:17,680 --> 00:15:21,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Let's not do that. 
Thank you for your counsel.</font>

233
00:15:21,670 --> 00:15:25,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noah, please continue to serve me 
as minister-prince of justice.</font>

234
00:15:26,650 --> 00:15:27,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

235
00:15:27,860 --> 00:15:29,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What shall we do with Cruz?</font>

236
00:15:30,380 --> 00:15:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His only crime is a lack of oversight.</font>

237
00:15:33,980 --> 00:15:36,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Six months of reduced pay should suffice.</font>

238
00:15:36,700 --> 00:15:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You heard him, Cruz.</font>

239
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:40,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See to it, as well.</font>

240
00:15:40,550 --> 00:15:42,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, Your Majesty!</font>

241
00:15:42,510 --> 00:15:44,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much!</font>

242
00:15:52,940 --> 00:15:54,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it done?</font>

243
00:15:54,540 --> 00:15:56,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since the man was a eunuch,</font>

244
00:15:56,770 --> 00:15:59,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I carried out his punishment personally.</font>

245
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:01,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And?</font>

246
00:16:01,210 --> 00:16:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Noah is remarkable.</font>

247
00:16:03,410 --> 00:16:07,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I almost wonder if he can read minds.</font>

248
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:09,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Albert...</font>

249
00:16:10,060 --> 00:16:11,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What will you do?</font>

250
00:16:11,580 --> 00:16:14,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... know not.</font>

251
00:16:17,210 --> 00:16:18,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoever he may be,</font>

252
00:16:18,880 --> 00:16:23,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even if I can't entrust the empire 
to him, he is still my son.</font>

253
00:16:27,210 --> 00:16:30,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incidentally, are you familiar 
with the name "Leviathan"?</font>

254
00:16:30,840 --> 00:16:33,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. He was one of the four sages</font>

255
00:16:33,170 --> 00:16:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who lent their powers to the 
emperor during the Silver Age.</font>

256
00:16:37,420 --> 00:16:42,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems that Leviathan is 
lending his powers to Noah now.</font>

257
00:16:42,450 --> 00:16:44,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that is splendid!</font>

258
00:16:44,170 --> 00:16:48,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If anyone can surpass the Silver Age,
perhaps it is Prince Noah!</font>

259
00:16:48,520 --> 00:16:51,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. He does have the 
potential, at least.</font>

260
00:16:52,500 --> 00:16:55,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will watch carefully</font>

261
00:16:55,190 --> 00:16:57,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to see how he grows from here.</font>

262
00:17:00,620 --> 00:17:02,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At your leave.</font>

263
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:11,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... Your Highness?</font>

264
00:17:11,260 --> 00:17:13,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are you heading from here?</font>

265
00:17:13,950 --> 00:17:18,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's unusual for you to insert 
yourself in conversations like this.</font>

266
00:17:18,700 --> 00:17:21,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm very sorry!</font>

267
00:17:21,010 --> 00:17:23,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just that you looked 
so lost in thought...</font>

268
00:17:23,290 --> 00:17:26,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. Your assessment is correct.</font>

269
00:17:26,180 --> 00:17:27,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then...</font>

270
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remain at ease.</font>

271
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We are indeed riding into a challenge, 
but our lives are not in danger.</font>

272
00:17:33,310 --> 00:17:34,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

273
00:17:34,770 --> 00:17:37,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're headed to my brother's,
the crown prince's, mansion.</font>

274
00:17:55,970 --> 00:17:59,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}High above in the clear blue sky</i></font>

275
00:17:59,830 --> 00:18:03,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The white birds are taking flight</i></font>

276
00:18:03,740 --> 00:18:08,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Signaling that a new wind has arrived</i></font>

277
00:18:07,510 --> 00:18:09,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, this is truly a rare visit.</font>

278
00:18:08,600 --> 00:18:11,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Singing to the town below</i></font>

279
00:18:10,010 --> 00:18:13,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't expecting the minister-prince 
of justice at the peak of his popularity.</font>

280
00:18:11,500 --> 00:18:13,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}In the heat of the busy city street</i></font>

281
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:15,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And the roaring voices of the crowd</i></font>

282
00:18:14,410 --> 00:18:17,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have come for an audience with 
Your Highness the Crown Prince.</font>

283
00:18:15,730 --> 00:18:17,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Everything that we have 
waited for is here</i></font>

284
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:23,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The door to a new age opens wide</i></font>

285
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:19,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please forgive me for 
visiting without notice.</font>

286
00:18:19,900 --> 00:18:22,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're always so formal.</font>

287
00:18:22,510 --> 00:18:25,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I suppose that's why you're 
the minister-prince of justice.</font>

288
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:26,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Holding on to just a single wish inside</i></font>

289
00:18:25,840 --> 00:18:29,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, relax.
Here, we're just two brothers.</font>

290
00:18:26,410 --> 00:18:29,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Counting all the freezing 
nights I have survived</i></font>

291
00:18:29,780 --> 00:18:31,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

292
00:18:32,280 --> 00:18:34,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stand by outside the mansion.</font>

293
00:18:34,480 --> 00:18:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

294
00:18:35,820 --> 00:18:40,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Having my guard wait outside is a show 
of my trust in the crown prince.</i></font>

295
00:18:40,790 --> 00:18:43,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sure Shirley understands that now.</i></font>

296
00:18:43,430 --> 00:18:46,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you prefer the
living room or the garden?</font>

297
00:18:46,010 --> 00:18:50,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've heard that your garden is kept 
by the renowned gardener, Torrant.</font>

298
00:18:50,480 --> 00:18:52,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been hoping for a chance to see it.</font>

299
00:18:52,980 --> 00:18:55,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yes, I never showed it to you, did I?</font>

300
00:18:55,950 --> 00:18:58,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very good. Right this way, then.</font>

301
00:18:59,270 --> 00:19:01,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's beautiful.</font>

302
00:19:01,230 --> 00:19:02,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can tell?</font>

303
00:19:03,210 --> 00:19:06,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. That tree with the 
double trunks, for example.</font>

304
00:19:06,230 --> 00:19:08,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never seen one so magnificent.</font>

305
00:19:08,630 --> 00:19:10,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your eyes are as keen as ever.</font>

306
00:19:10,740 --> 00:19:13,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was a gift from a member of my 
household that I sent away to work.</font>

307
00:19:13,840 --> 00:19:15,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It cost 50,000 rean, apparently.</font>

308
00:19:15,950 --> 00:19:18,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can believe that.</font>

309
00:19:18,060 --> 00:19:20,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll have it sent to your mansion later.</font>

310
00:19:22,290 --> 00:19:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You saw its quality with one look.</font>

311
00:19:24,710 --> 00:19:28,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The tree itself would be happier 
with a man who understands it.</font>

312
00:19:28,220 --> 00:19:30,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I will gratefully accept it.</font>

313
00:19:30,900 --> 00:19:34,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This will be the second time I've 
personally given you something.</font>

314
00:19:34,800 --> 00:19:38,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem to have mastered 
that magic sword, no?</font>

315
00:19:38,570 --> 00:19:41,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only gave it to you as a little joke,</font>

316
00:19:41,190 --> 00:19:43,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but that has taught me</font>

317
00:19:43,280 --> 00:19:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that great power only belongs in 
the hands of the right people.</font>

318
00:19:53,380 --> 00:19:56,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Summer is upon us again.</font>

319
00:19:56,390 --> 00:19:57,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm? Yes.</font>

320
00:19:58,320 --> 00:20:00,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I asked earlier,</font>

321
00:20:00,780 --> 00:20:03,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and His Majesty said he will travel north 
to escape the heat again this year.</font>

322
00:20:03,960 --> 00:20:05,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What differs from previous years</font>

323
00:20:06,380 --> 00:20:08,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is that he intends to take 
you with him this year.</font>

324
00:20:10,310 --> 00:20:11,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In recent years,</i></font>

325
00:20:11,630 --> 00:20:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>when the emperor left the 
capital to escape the heat,</i></font>

326
00:20:14,830 --> 00:20:17,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>he had the crown prince 
rule in his stead.</i></font>

327
00:20:18,790 --> 00:20:22,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This allowed him to gradually give the 
crown prince more government duties</i></font>

328
00:20:22,680 --> 00:20:25,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>as a rehearsal for his 
future reign as emperor.</i></font>

329
00:20:26,370 --> 00:20:28,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But doing away with that means...</i></font>

330
00:20:28,950 --> 00:20:30,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How much...</font>

331
00:20:30,880 --> 00:20:32,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">do you know?</font>

332
00:20:33,220 --> 00:20:36,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Majesty only gave me 
a roundabout explanation.</font>

333
00:20:36,350 --> 00:20:42,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said he wanted to give you a thorough 
education on the essence of ruling.</font>

334
00:20:42,170 --> 00:20:43,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I beg your pardon?</font>

335
00:20:43,630 --> 00:20:46,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He is the kind of great ruler 
we see only once a millennia.</font>

336
00:20:46,840 --> 00:20:51,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I imagine he has come up with many 
methods that we could never even imagine.</font>

337
00:20:52,600 --> 00:20:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can only guess that he wants 
to teach them to you now.</font>

338
00:20:57,370 --> 00:21:00,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His Majesty does intend 
to take Albert with him,</i></font>

339
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:04,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but probably only because keeping him 
close means one less thing to worry about.</i></font>

340
00:21:05,870 --> 00:21:07,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even so,</i></font>

341
00:21:07,240 --> 00:21:08,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>if spending time together</i></font>

342
00:21:08,910 --> 00:21:12,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>helps my brother understand
His Majesty's feelings...</i></font>

343
00:21:13,320 --> 00:21:16,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. Thank you, Noah.</font>

344
00:21:31,480 --> 00:21:32,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

345
00:21:32,570 --> 00:21:33,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Alichey.</font>

346
00:21:34,020 --> 00:21:36,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm up next, so I came to greet you.</font>

347
00:21:36,570 --> 00:21:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

348
00:21:39,960 --> 00:21:41,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

349
00:21:41,430 --> 00:21:44,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing. I will sing 
with all I have in me,</font>

350
00:21:44,670 --> 00:21:47,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">just like you told me to.</font>

351
00:21:47,730 --> 00:21:48,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good.</font>

352
00:21:55,240 --> 00:22:00,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Sweetly echoing my mother's lullaby</i></font>

353
00:22:00,850 --> 00:22:06,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Orange fire casting shadows on the wall</i></font>

354
00:22:06,670 --> 00:22:11,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Feigning sleep I held on 
tight to father's back</i></font>

355
00:22:11,370 --> 00:22:15,700
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#c4c4c4"><font size="10">Translation:
Timing:
Editing:
Quality Control:</font></font></b></font></font>

356
00:22:11,370 --> 00:22:15,700
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#c4c4c4"><font size="10">Becky Cottrill
Edgar Cruz
Gabriella Alabanza
S Bilyeu</font></font></b></font></font>

357
00:22:11,510 --> 00:22:15,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Safe in his arms</i></font>

358
00:22:15,540 --> 00:22:19,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}You must be strong</i></font>

359
00:22:19,340 --> 00:22:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}To protect the weak</i></font>

360
00:22:24,420 --> 00:22:26,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I know this truth well</i></font>

361
00:22:26,370 --> 00:22:32,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Because he taught me so</i></font>

362
00:22:32,090 --> 00:22:36,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Crying in frustration</i></font>

363
00:22:36,030 --> 00:22:39,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}My tears become a river now</i></font>

364
00:22:39,770 --> 00:22:49,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Carrying hope to tomorrow</i></font>

365
00:22:44,250 --> 00:22:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enter.</font>

366
00:22:45,780 --> 00:22:47,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon me, Master.</font>

367
00:22:49,520 --> 00:22:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm sorry to visit so late at night.</font>

368
00:22:52,600 --> 00:22:56,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}There is a woman here 
who wishes to see you.</font>

369
00:22:57,470 --> 00:22:58,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Her name?</font>

370
00:22:58,510 --> 00:23:00,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Olivia Coil.</font>

371
00:23:00,930 --> 00:23:02,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't know that name.</i></font>

372
00:23:02,730 --> 00:23:07,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But if she wasn't someone important, 
Zoey would have sent her away.</i></font>

373
00:23:07,600 --> 00:23:08,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine. Let her in.</font>

374
00:23:10,190 --> 00:23:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said your name is Olivia?</font>

375
00:23:12,690 --> 00:23:21,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}There is nothing we can 
take when we depart</i></font>

376
00:23:13,010 --> 00:23:15,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is your business
here at this hour?</font>

377
00:23:15,150 --> 00:23:16,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bring you a tip.</font>

378
00:23:17,430 --> 00:23:20,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The crown prince, Second Prince Albert,</font>

379
00:23:21,280 --> 00:23:25,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Blooming in the glory</i></font>

380
00:23:22,690 --> 00:23:24,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">plans to lead
a coup tonight...</font>

381
00:23:25,050 --> 00:23:30,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}For the future I had always dreamed of</i></font>

382
00:23:30,260 --> 00:23:32,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I will stand right here</i></font>

383
00:23:31,380 --> 00:23:34,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and force His Majesty 
to abdicate the throne.</font>

384
00:23:32,240 --> 00:23:38,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Singing out a song of blessing</i></font>

